SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM positiemutaties_geld a INNER JOIN transakties b ON a.pmg_tr_volgnummer=b.tr_volgnummer INNER JOIN rekeningen_per_product c ON a.pmg_relatienr =c.rpp_relatienummer AND a.pmg_rekeningnr =c.rpp_rekening_nummer AND a.pmg_rekening_soort =c.rpp_rekeningsoort AND a.pmg_rekening_munts =c.rpp_valuta WHERE a.pmg_relatienr BETWEEN ~1 AND ~2 AND a.pmg_rekening_soort BETWEEN ~3 AND ~4 AND a.pmg_boekdatum BETWEEN ~5 AND ~6 AND c.rpp_productnummer BETWEEN ~7 AND ~8

SELECT a.pmg_relatienr , a.pmg_rekeningnr , a.pmg_rekening_soort, a.pmg_rekening_munts, a.pmg_mutatie_aantal, a.pmg_boekdatum , a.pmg_valutadatum , a.pmg_tr_volgnummer , a.pmg_saldo_boekdatum , b.tr_mut_gemaakt , b.tr_mutatiecode , c.rpp_productnummer , c.rpp_volgnr_per_product FROM positiemutaties_geld a INNER JOIN transakties b ON a.pmg_tr_volgnummer=b.tr_volgnummer INNER JOIN rekeningen_per_product c ON a.pmg_relatienr =c.rpp_relatienummer AND a.pmg_rekeningnr =c.rpp_rekening_nummer AND a.pmg_rekening_soort =c.rpp_rekeningsoort AND a.pmg_rekening_munts =c.rpp_valuta WHERE a.pmg_relatienr BETWEEN ~1 AND ~2 AND a.pmg_rekening_soort BETWEEN ~3 AND ~4 AND a.pmg_boekdatum BETWEEN ~5 AND ~6 AND c.rpp_productnummer BETWEEN ~7 AND ~8 ORDER BY a.pmg_relatienr , a.pmg_rekening_soort, a.pmg_rekening_munts, a.pmg_rekeningnr , a.pmg_boekdatum, a.pmg_transactienr, a.pmg_schemaregel
